data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 2020-built home boasting elegance and comfort at every turn! Step into the grand, 2-story foyer, setting the stage for the luxurious interiors that await. The main level features a formal dining room and a cozy family room complete with a fireplace - perfect for gatherings or quiet evenings. The heart of the home lies in the spacious chef's kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances, a double oven, and elegant lighting that accentuates the beautiful white cabinets. Upstairs, discover 4 large bedrooms, alongside a palatial primary suite featuring a sitting area, dual walk-in closets, tray ceiling, and an owner's bathroom complete with a rejuvenating soaking tub and private toilet area. Step outside to the level backyard offering privacy and space to entertain guests - perfect for summer cookouts or peaceful relaxation. The second-floor Owner's suite presents a large bedroom with a generous sitting area, dual vanities, and a separate shower, providing the ultimate retreat. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your new home sweet home! For more information or to schedule a showing, contact us today!-
